- Requires bd-3saj (test infrastructure)
- Requires bd-12hi (cargo compilation produces output to verify)","status":"open","priority":1,"issue_type":"feature","created_at":"2026-01-19T18:21:13.741339923Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-19T18:40:42.625937337Z","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-2ga8","depends_on_id":"bd-12hi","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-19T18:21:21.565575304Z","created_by":"ubuntu"},{"issue_id":"bd-2ga8","depends_on_id":"bd-1cwg","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-19T18:21:19.052702518Z","created_by":"ubuntu"},{"issue_id":"bd-2ga8","depends_on_id":"bd-3saj","type":"blocks","created_at":"2026-01-19T18:21:20.652641255Z","created_by":"ubuntu"}]}
